# Project: elder-guardian-ai
Elder financial-exploitation early-warning web app. CSV upload -> LangGraph
multi-agent pipeline -> risk score -> (if >65) Claude narrative + SMS + email alert.
Stack: Next.js 14 App Router + TypeScript + Tailwind + shadcn/ui (Recharts),
FastAPI, LangGraph, scikit-learn / PyTorch / NetworkX / SHAP,
Supabase (Postgres + Auth), Twilio, Resend.

## Always
- Never invent or guess a library API. Check the installed package source or lockfile before using any function.
- Every API endpoint validates input and returns a structured error (status + message). Never leave an unhandled 500.
- Secrets in environment variables only. Never hardcode keys or write them into committed files.
- Small, reviewable changes. One-line comment on any non-obvious decision.
